<td>July 03, 2012</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="4">The dead body of Daniel Thalbrum was discovered in a ditch by the side of Interstate 499. Police have ruled the cause of death as a suicide. His car was recovered in a junkyard, and contained a suicide note detailing alleged &quot;betrayal&quot; from Marshall, Carter and Dark. The note also mentioned a lack of any royalties for the &quot;Thalbrum Vehicle Security System&quot; from MC&amp;D.<br />
<br />
The news of his death resulted in outrage from the media, and sales of the item have dropped drastically.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="4">Marshall, Carter and Dark, LLP</th>
</tr>
